cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.MM, cs.LG

This paper deals with computer vision and deep learning techniques to estimate foot pressure heatmaps from 2D human pose derived from video frames. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions potential applications in kinesiology, medicine, sports, and robotics, indicating that it could also belong to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.RO (Robotics). The use of deep learning models for regression tasks suggests that it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
